# 🏗️ System Architecture

```text
                         ┌───────────────┐
                         │     Admin     │
                         └───────┬───────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
                       Create Campaign
                                 │
                                 ▼
                        Campaign Service
                                 │
                                 ▼
                      Find Matching Users
                                 │
                                 ▼
                           BullMQ Queue
                                 │
                                 ▼
                              Redis
                                 │
                                 ▼
                              Worker
                                 │
                                 ▼
                         Email Service
                                 │
                                 ▼
                              Resend
                                 │
                                 ▼
                           User Inbox
```

---

# 🏛️ Layered Architecture

```text
Routes
   │
   ▼
Controllers
   │
   ▼
Services
   │
   ▼
Repositories
   │
   ▼
PostgreSQL
```

### Responsibilities

#### Routes

Receive HTTP Requests

#### Controllers

Handle Request & Response

#### Services

Business Logic

#### Repositories

Database Queries

