# ⚡ BullMQ Workflow

```text
Campaign Service
       │
       ▼
queueEmail()
       │
       ▼
BullMQ Queue
       │
       ▼
Redis
       │
       ▼
Worker
       │
       ▼
Email Service
       │
       ▼
Resend
```

---

# 🔁 Retry Strategy

Each email job is configured with:

```javascript
attempts: 3

backoff: {
  type: "exponential",
  delay: 5000
}
```

Example:

```text
Attempt 1
   ↓
Fail
   ↓
5 Seconds

Attempt 2
   ↓
Fail
   ↓
10 Seconds

Attempt 3
   ↓
Fail
   ↓
Marked Failed
```

---

# 🚀 Running The Project

## Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

## Configure Environment

```env
DATABASE_URL=

JWT_SECRET=

CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=

RESEND_API_KEY=
```

## Start Backend

```bash
npm run dev
```

## Start Worker

```bash
node worker.js
```

